      <t>This document describes how E-VPN can be used as an NVO solution and explores the various tunnel encapsulation options and their impact on the E-VPN control-plane and procedures. In particular, the following encapsulation options are analyzed: MPLS over GRE, VXLAN, and NVGRE.</t>
